org.cef.handler

类 CefPrintHandlerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.callback.CefNativeAdapter
      • org.cef.handler.CefPrintHandlerAdapter
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    CefNative, CefPrintHandler 

    public abstract class CefPrintHandlerAdapter
extends CefNativeAdapter
implements CefPrintHandler
    An abstract adapter class for receiving print events on Linux. The methods in this class are empty. This class exists as convenience for creating handler objects. (用于在Linux上接收打印事件的抽象适配器类。此类中的方法为空。此类的存在是为了方便创建处理程序对象。)

      • getPdfPaperSize

        public java.awt.Dimension getPdfPaperSize(int deviceUnitsPerInch)
        从接口复制的说明: CefPrintHandler
        Called to retrieve the page size when printToPDF is requested for a browser. (当浏览器请求printToPDF时，调用此方法来检索页面大小。)
        指定者:
        getPdfPaperSize 在接口中  CefPrintHandler
        参数:
        deviceUnitsPerInch - The DPI of the print. Use this to calculate the page size to use. (-打印的DPI。使用它来计算要使用的页面大小。)
        返回:
        The page size in microns. (页面大小（以微米为单位）。)

      • onPrintDialog

        public boolean onPrintDialog(CefBrowser browser,
                             boolean hasSelection,
                             CefPrintDialogCallback callback)
        从接口复制的说明: CefPrintHandler
        Called to show the print dialog. (调用以显示打印对话框。)
        指定者:
        onPrintDialog 在接口中  CefPrintHandler
        参数:
        browser - The corresponding browser. (-相应的浏览器。)
        hasSelection - True if the user has selected a region of the page to print. (-如果用户选择了要打印的页面区域，则为True。)
        callback - Callback to execute after the dialog is dismissed. (-取消对话框后执行回调。)
        返回:
        True if the dialog will be displayed or false to cancel the printing immediately. (如果将显示对话框，则为True，否则为false，以立即取消打印。)

      • onPrintJob

        public boolean onPrintJob(CefBrowser browser,
                          java.lang.String documentName,
                          java.lang.String pdfFilePath,
                          CefPrintJobCallback callback)
        从接口复制的说明: CefPrintHandler
        Called to send the print job to the printer. (调用以将打印作业发送到打印机。)
        指定者:
        onPrintJob 在接口中  CefPrintHandler
        参数:
        browser - The corresponding browser. (-相应的浏览器。)
        documentName - Name of the document that is printing. (-正在打印的文档名称。)
        pdfFilePath - Path to the PDF file that contains the document contents. (-包含文档内容的PDF文件的路径。)
        callback - Callback to execute after the print job has completed. (-打印作业完成后执行回调。)
        返回:
        True if the job will proceed or false to cancel the printing immediately. (如果作业将继续，则为True，否则为false，以立即取消打印。)

        从接口复制的说明: CefPrintHandler

      • onPrintStart

        public void onPrintStart(CefBrowser browser)
        从接口复制的说明: CefPrintHandler
        Called when printing has started. This method will be called before the other onPrint*() methods and irrespective of how printing was initiated (e.g. CefBrowser::print(), JavaScript window.print() or PDF extension print button). (开始打印时调用。该方法将在其他onPrint *（）方法之前调用，并且无论如何启动打印（例如CefBrowser :: print（），JavaScript window.print（）或PDF扩展打印按钮）。)
        指定者:
        onPrintStart 在接口中  CefPrintHandler
        参数:
        browser - The corresponding browser. (-相应的浏览器。)
